- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper discusses the use of a camera phone to improve an exploration system for astrobiology and geology, which involves robotics and automation. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper mentions the development and testing of computer-vision algorithms for planetary exploration using the camera phone. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of computer-vision algorithms and machine learning techniques for planetary exploration falls under this category. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper may involve natural language processing techniques for analyzing and interpreting data collected during planetary exploration. 
- cs.GR (Graphics): The paper may involve the visualization and rendering of data collected during planetary exploration.
